  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd - \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Problem in Coding Implementation - Petrol Station Owners Association",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Q. R. Petrol station owners' associations point out that implementing the code system and taking mobile phones to petrol stations will have massive consequences and there is a practical problem and insurance companies have said that the insurance coverage of petrol stations will be cancelled.",
        "Sibetco of the country and Lanka I.O.C. Q at fuel stations also from 21st. R. It was said that fuel can be obtained through the code.",
        "However, petrol stations are apprehensive about implementing this system as insurance companies have said that they are facing problems in getting insurance coverage.",
        "These two measures cannot be implemented in practice and the Fuel Filling Station Owners Association is discussing about taking an alternative measure.",
        "Meanwhile, QR A senior official of the Ministry of Energy said that the date of supply of fuel by the code and the last digit of the vehicle registration number plate has been postponed indefinitely."
      ],
